CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall"
TitMainTitle: Women, including one in foreground wearing light colored dress, heart necklace, and eyeglasses, and men, seated at banquet tables in Webster Hall for event honoring Daisy Lampkin
